<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of Article 17 of the Act Governing Food Safety and Sanitation.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This standard applies to bottled and packaged drinking water which is suitable for human consumption.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The maximum level of microorganism (Only applied to bottled and packaged drinking water which is suitable for direct consumption):
┌────────────┬──────────┐
│Microorganism           │Limit               │
├────────────┼──────────┤
│Coliform bacteria       │Negative            │
├────────────┼──────────┤
│Fecal Streptococci      │Negative            │
├────────────┼──────────┤
│Pseudomonas aeruginosa  │Negative            │
└────────────┴──────────┘]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard shall be implemented at release date.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
